，尋求自我保障的方法，以免跌進警方的陷阱，誤墮法網！ 轉貼"},{"pid":"755141f25255c54ef108bca9a646f919726f784b","tid":1001414,"uid":223326,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"6a46a0e5d3042b113dc0de3f0cafba71447299e9","tid":1001414,"uid":33972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3cbfc8fdc8d3497c3e1349fe42978d80d46e13f","tid":1001414,"uid":223326,"like":68,"dislike":2,"score":66,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:43:24.000Z","msg":"警方去左5次，每次逗留左超過3小時。<br />\n<br />\n又話對波唔渣唔得，<br />\n<br />\n即係如果女警放蛇捉嫖客，都一定要屌埋女警啦！ 唔屌唔得啊嘛！<br />\n<br />\n即係要同一個女警要放蛇同一個嫖客5次，每次性接觸3小時，先得啦！<br />\n<br />\n不可以雙重標准wo！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:55:25.000Z","msg":"嫖客好似冇犯法喎，除非個女警唔夠16歲啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:08:27.000Z","msg":"除非1樓1算無犯法。其他任何叫雞形式包括上網叫援交雞是犯法"},{"pid":"a38c67d6847382a36988ef93caf4cf6df8b429b5","tid":1001414,"uid":10757,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"f31346f2c75e166b09dad91d5e71bbcd9027c1ec","tid":1001414,"uid":38049,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T07:08:42.000Z","msg":"事後發現全場無泰妹"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:10:49.000Z","msg":"碌鳩已漸痕 銀行提現金1000蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a700d2f4b2ed1f22e5e115271e521c34d16e75e","tid":1001414,"uid":3656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"755141f25255c54ef108bca9a646f919726f784b","tid":1001414,"uid":223326,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"6a46a0e5d3042b113dc0de3f0cafba71447299e9","tid":1001414,"uid":33972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3cbfc8fdc8d3497c3e1349fe42978d80d46e13f","tid":1001414,"uid":223326,"like":68,"dislike":2,"score":66,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:43:24.000Z","msg":"警方去左5次，每次逗留左超過3小時。<br />\n<br />\n又話對波唔渣唔得，<br />\n<br />\n即係如果女警放蛇捉嫖客，都一定要屌埋女警啦！ 唔屌唔得啊嘛！<br />\n<br />\n即係要同一個女警要放蛇同一個嫖客5次，每次性接觸3小時，先得啦！<br />\n<br />\n不可以雙重標准w